refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 public Ds\SequenceDs\Map::pairs




  Returns a Ds\Sequence containing all the pairs of the map.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Ds\Map::pairs example


<?php
$map = new \Ds\Map(["a" => 1, "b" => 2, "c" => 3]);

var_dump($map->pairs());
?>


